Package: academicCVtools
Type: Package
Title: Tools to Generate Academic CV Sections from Google Sheets for Typst/Quarto
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Oliver",
           family = "Rehren",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "o.rehren@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7602-8219")) 
Description: Provides functions to read structured data for academic CVs 
    (like publications, work experience, education) from individual sheets 
    within a Google Sheets document. Handles potentially variable sheet and 
    column names. Includes tools to transform this data into Typst function 
    calls, suitable for integration into Quarto documents using a Typst template 
    workflow. Facilitates the creation of automated, data-driven academic CVs.
